# User Guide

## Master Lookup
Use the Master Lookup screen to search by LWH ID, customer, item, lot, bay, or other visible/customer-specific fields. Data auto-loads when the app opens; use Load / Refresh Data if you need the very latest sheet changes right away.

## Receiving / InvRec Print
Enter an InvRec value to find all associated pallets and print labels in bulk. Also auto-loads on open.

## Camera Scanner
Tap Camera Scan on Master Lookup or Master Lookup's search screens. Works on iPhone/Safari and Android Chrome/Edge.

## Printing
Use browser print preview to confirm orientation and scale before printing to Zebra.
